I lost track of who's there or not.

::Kluster::

Kluster frowns, looking over at Whistler. "You may sit at any of the 
seats at the table. Catch a few winks if you'd like," he says, 
motioning to the table, which had lots of empty seats. It was 
designed for the whole crew of the Cybertronian Fire (50 bots, 40 of 
which died during landing).

He looks at Lunarpine. "As soon as Iron Raptor gets here, we'll 
begin. You can get to know the Maximals around here if you wish."

just

and everyone

less sleep.

I?  I 
> guess I should stop talking now."
